  "texts": [
    "Relevant factors are whether the misuse is socially accepted and whether the user was gravely at fault (Vansweevelt & Weyts, 2009, 517).",
    "The previous sections have examined legal criteria for defining product defects in the EU and the U.S. in light of economic considerations.",
    "The next focus is on the unique challenges that arise when applying these criteria to AI systems, considering the distinct characteristics of AI.",
    "AI encompasses a spectrum of technologies that can be employed in a wide range of sectors and contexts.",
    "55 This means that the dimensions of AI safety, or conversely, of AI risks, depend on the type of technology and the context in which it is used."
